TITLE: Implementing Sum Function Using While Loop in Move
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use a while loop to compute the sum of numbers from 1 to n in Move. It uses mutable variables to keep track of the sum and the current number.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/move-book/blob/main/reference/src/control-flow/loops.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
fun sum(n: u64): u64 {
    let mut sum = 0;
    let mut i = 1;
    while (i <= n) {
        sum = sum + i;
        i = i + 1
    };

    sum
}
```

