TITLE: For Reference Macro Implementation in Move
DESCRIPTION: Macro implementation for iterating over vector elements, used to demonstrate labeled control flow with macros.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/move-book/blob/main/reference/src/control-flow/labeled-control-flow.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
macro fun for_ref<$T>($vs: &vector<$T>, $f: |&$T|) {
    let vs = $vs;
    let mut i = 0;
    let end = vs.length();
    while (i < end) {
        $f(vs.borrow(i));
        i = i + 1;
    }
}
```

