TITLE: Calling Package Visibility Functions from Within the Same Package
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to call a package-visible function from another module within the same package. This is allowed as package-visible functions are accessible to all modules in the same package.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/move-book/blob/main/book/src/move-basics/visibility.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
module book::try_calling_package;

use book::package_visibility;

// Same package `book` -> can call package_only()
fun try_calling_package() {
    package_visibility::package_only();
}
```

