TITLE: Replacing 'friend' with 'public(package)' in Move 2024
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to replace the deprecated 'friend' keyword with the new 'public(package)' visibility modifier for functions in Move 2024.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/move-book/blob/main/book/src/guides/2024-migration-guide.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: move
CODE:
```
// Move 2020
friend book::friend_module;
public(friend) fun protected_function() {}

// Move 2024
public(package) fun protected_function_2024() {}
```

