TITLE: Transferring Objects to Sender in Sui CLI
DESCRIPTION: Command syntax for transferring a list of objects to the sender in Sui CLI. This command is used to move ownership of objects to the specified address.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mystenlabs/move-book/blob/main/book/src/your-first-move/hello-sui.md#2025-04-22_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
--transfer-objects "[list]" sender
```

